                           <rs type="person" ref="pe__andreas_chrannest_QGW_II_I_319"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Andres des Chrannestes chaplan, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__ruprechtshofen-pfarre">pharrer</roleName> zu
